com.stripe.android.model

Class Card

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stripe.model.StripeObject
      • com.stripe.android.model.Card

  • public class Card
extends com.stripe.model.StripeObject
    A model object representing a Card in the Android SDK. Note that this is slightly different from the Card model in stripe-java.
